factor_expression: (($open - DELAY($close, 1)) / (TS_MEAN(MAX($high - $low, MAX(ABS($high - DELAY($close, 1)), ABS($low - DELAY($close, 1)))), 5) + 1e-8)) * (TS_STD($return, 20) / ((TS_MAX($high, 10) - TS_MIN($low, 10)) * TS_STD($volume, 10) + 1e-8))
